             were indicted for <rs id="t18141026-66-off370" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18141026-66-off370" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18141026-66-off370" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18141026-66-victim641" type="victimName">
                           Mary 
                           Howell
                        <interp inst="t18141026-66-victim641" type="surname" value="Howell"></interp>
