            . I am an officer of Bow-street. Upon Beck being brought to Bow-street, this key was given to me by a gentleman of the name of Meaken, in the presence of Banks. I took the key afterwards to Mr. Wilson's house; I found it opened the street door with a great deal more ease than I could with their own key.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18141026-66-person664">
                  THOMAS 
                  CAVE
               <interp inst="t18141026-66-person664" type="surname" value="CAVE"></interp>
